  tmenu         ToolBar.TrimSpaces      Remove trailing whitespace
  amenu 1.202   ToolBar.ToggleHdr       <C-F6>
  tmenu         ToolBar.ToggleHdr       Switch between source and header (C/C++), or code and test (Python)
